{"name": "mailstream", "metadata": {"name": "mailstream", "version": "0.1.0", "classifiers": [], "home_page": "https://github.com/christianobora/mailstream", "license": null, "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["aioimaplib"], "summary": "Async IMAP client for streaming email messages", "upload_time": 1733453063}, "documentation": ["# Mailstream\n\n## Overview\n\nMailStream is an asynchronous IMAP email client built with `aioimaplib`. It supports streaming emails, polling for updates, and broadcasting new emails to listeners.\n\n## Features\n\n- Asynchronous IMAP connection\n- Fetch unseen emails\n- Broadcast new emails to subscribers\n- Easily integrate with context management\n\n## Installation\n\n```bash\npip install mailstream\n```\n\n## Quick Start\n\n```python\nimport asyncio\nfrom mailstream import MailStreamClient, Config\n\nasync def process_email(mail):\n    print(f\"New email from: {mail.from_email}\")\n    print(f\"Subject: {mail.subject}\")\n\nconfig = Config(\n    host=\"imap.example.com\",\n    port=993,\n    email=\"your_email@example.com\",\n    password=\"your_password\"\n)\n\nasync def main():\n    client = MailStreamClient(config)\n    await client.connect()\n\n    # Subscribe to new emails\n    listener = client.subscribe()\n    \n    # Process emails from listener\n    while True:\n        mail = await listener.get()\n        await process_email(mail)\n\n    # Close connection\n    await client.close()\n\nasyncio.run(main())\n```\n\n## Configuration Options\n\n- `host`: IMAP server hostname (required)\n- `email`: Login email (required)\n- `password`: Login password (required)\n- `port`: IMAP server port (default: 993)\n- `mailbox`: Target mailbox (default: 'INBOX')\n\n## Advanced Usage\n\n### Fetching Unseen Mails\n\n```python\n# Retrieve all unseen emails\nunseen_mails = client.get_unseen_mails()\nfor mail in unseen_mails:\n    print(mail.subject)\n```\n\n### Multiple Listeners\n\n```python\nasync def listener1(mail):\n    print(\"Listener 1 received:\", mail.subject)\n\nasync def listener2(mail):\n    print(\"Listener 2 received:\", mail.subject)\n\nlistener1_queue = client.subscribe()\nlistener2_queue = client.subscribe()\n```\n\n### Waiting for New Emails\n\n```python\nawait client.wait_for_updates(poll_interval=10.0)\n```\n\n## Error Handling\n\n```python\nfrom mailstream import ConnectionError, AuthenticationError\n\ntry:\n    client = MailStreamClient(\n        host='imap.example.com',\n        email='your_email@example.com',\n        password='your_password'\n    )\n    await client.connect()\nexcept (ConnectionError, AuthenticationError) as e:\n    print(f\"Connection failed: {e}\")\n```\n\n## Contributing\n\nContributions are welcome! Please see our contributing guidelines for more details.\n\n## License\n\n[MIT](LICENSE)\n\n## Support\n\nFor issues, please open a GitHub issue in the repository.\n"], "modules": [{"name": "mailstream.exceptions", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [{"name": "mailstream.exceptions.MailStreamError", "bases": ["Exception"], "methods": [], "class_variables": [], "instance_variables": [], "inner_classes": [], "documentation": ["Base exception for mailstream package"]}, {"name": "mailstream.exceptions.ConnectionError", "bases": ["MailStreamError"], "methods": [], "class_variables": [], "instance_variables": [], "inner_classes": [], "documentation": ["Error during IMAP connection"]}, {"name": "mailstream.exceptions.AuthenticationError", "bases": ["MailStreamError"], "methods": [], "class_variables": [], "instance_variables": [], "inner_classes": [], "documentation": ["Authentication failed"]}, {"name": "mailstream.exceptions.FetchError", "bases": ["MailStreamError"], "methods": [], "class_variables": [], "instance_variables": [], "inner_classes": [], "documentation": ["Error fetching emails"]}, {"name": "mailstream.exceptions.AlreadyWaitingError", "bases": ["MailStreamError"], "methods": [], "class_variables": [], "instance_variables": [], "inner_classes": [], "documentation": ["Already waiting for updates"]}], "exports": []}, {"name": "mailstream.context", "documentation": [], "functions": [{"name": "mailstream.context.with_mailstream", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "client", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["Add mailstream client to context"]}, {"name": "mailstream.context.from_mailstream", "asynchronous": false, "params": [], "returns": null, "documentation": ["Retrieve mailstream client from context"]}], "variables": [{"name": "mailstream.context._mailstream_context", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "mailstream", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": [{"name": "mailstream.AlreadyWaitingError", "xref": {"fqname": "mailstream.exceptions.AlreadyWaitingError", "project": null}}, {"name": "mailstream.AuthenticationError", "xref": {"fqname": "mailstream.exceptions.AuthenticationError", "project": null}}, {"name": "mailstream.Config", "xref": {"fqname": "mailstream.client.Config", "project": null}}, {"name": "mailstream.ConnectionError", "xref": {"fqname": "mailstream.exceptions.ConnectionError", "project": null}}, {"name": "mailstream.FetchError", "xref": {"fqname": "mailstream.exceptions.FetchError", "project": null}}, {"name": "mailstream.from_mailstream", "xref": {"fqname": "mailstream.context.from_mailstream", "project": null}}, {"name": "mailstream.Mail", "xref": {"fqname": "mailstream.mail.Mail", "project": null}}, {"name": "mailstream.MailStreamClient", "xref": {"fqname": "mailstream.client.MailStreamClient", "project": null}}, {"name": "mailstream.MailStreamError", "xref": {"fqname": "mailstream.exceptions.MailStreamError", "project": null}}, {"name": "mailstream.with_mailstream", "xref": {"fqname": "mailstream.context.with_mailstream", "project": null}}]}, {"name": "mailstream.mail", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [{"n